Software Setup
=================================
MACOS Ventura 13.2.1
Xcode 14.2
Expo Version => (#expo -v) ==> 0.6.2
Tested on IOS Simulator Iphone 14 / IOS 16.2
Tested on Android Xiaomi 11T Iphone 14 / Android 12

TechStack
=================================
React Native Reanimated
React Native Gesture Handler
React Native Skia
Flashlist


**************************************
FAMILY INPUT PROJECT (Animated Text Input)
**************************************

Features
=================================
Animate when Adding a new character
Animate before destroying an AnimatedTextComponent
Auto calculate positions & center drawing on Canvas area
Auto adjust fontSize when #of inputs are likely not fitting into screen

Animations Used
=================================
opacity and x/y axis related animations




**************************************
DRAG AND DROP PROJECT (Animated Drag and Drop)
**************************************

Features
=================================
Draggable Flashlist Images with column size and vertical margin between each row are adjustable.
